= Overview =

The bladeRF stream consists of blocks of samples that are multiples of 1024 samples (4096 bytes) in size. When metadata is enabled, the first ''N'' samples of a block are replaced with metadata.

The below table depicts this metadata. All fields are in little-endian byte order.

